Description: KBAscope provides user-friendly functions for editing species 
              data (population, range maps, area of occupancy, area of habitat 
              and localities), applying Key Biodiversity Areas criteria and 
              generating spatial and summary outputs that can be used in 
              national workshops to help propose Key Biodiversity Areas in a 
              country.
